2. (9) pursue, follow -- (follow in or as if in pursuit; "The police car pursued the suspected attacker"; "Her bad deed followed her and haunted her dreams all her life")
3. (6) quest for, go after, quest after, pursue -- (go in search of or hunt for; "pursue a hobby")
